data.description: Absolutely darling home in a prime location just a short walk or bike ride to Lester Park and some of the many great hiking and biking trails that Duluth has to offer! This home features a welcoming living room with beautiful hardwood floors, kitchen with breakfast bar, 2 bedrooms, and a full bath on the main level. Downstairs is a rec room (could be converted to a 3rd legal bedroom with the addition of an egress window), laundry, and storage. Don't miss the big back deck, plentiful off street parking, and 24 x 26 garage!
